      "author": "kirangathani",
      "description": "### Fixed\n\n- **Ghost comments after deletion**: Comments that were deleted would reappear as empty \"(no note yet)\" entries when reopening the PDF. The sidecar JSON was not being saved on view close because `super.onClose()` nulled the file reference before the save ran. Deletion commits now run before teardown and are properly awaited.\n- **Orphaned annotation cleanup**: On load, annotations whose backing note no longer exists are now pruned from the sidecar automatically.\n- **Long word wrapping in comment preview**: Unbroken words/strings that exceed the comment preview width now wrap instead of overflowing on a single line.",
      "downloadCount": 10,
      "draft": false,
      "name": "1.3.1",
      "prerelease": false,
      "publishedAt": "2026-04-06T20:16:24Z",
      "tag": "1.3.1"
