      "author": "kirangathani",
      "description": "### Improved\n\n- **Search performance**: Rewritten to use inline `<mark>` elements instead of absolutely-positioned overlay divs. Eliminates layout thrashing — typing in the search bar is now instant. Added 150ms input debounce.\n- **Comment selection**: Clicking between comments now swaps editor/preview in-place on only the affected markers instead of rebuilding the entire pane. Removes the flash and delay when switching comments.\n- **Cursor placement**: Caret now lands at the end of the comment text rather than on a trailing blank line.",
      "downloadCount": 1,
