      "author": "kirangathani",
      "description": "### Fixed\n\n- Comment notes no longer lose frontmatter and PDF backlink on save. The `doSave()` closure now syncs dataset fields from the on-disk note before writing, preventing the background-created frontmatter and Source backlink from being clobbered.\n- Comment pane preview no longer displays the Source backlink line — it remains in the note file only, visible and clickable when opening the note directly.",
