      "author": "kirangathani",
      "description": "## What's new\n\n- **PDF backlink in comment notes** — each comment note now includes a clickable wikilink back to the source PDF with page number, separated from the comment body by a horizontal rule\n- **Rename PDF from viewer** — click the pencil icon or double-click the title to rename; cascades updates to the sidecar file, comment folder, and all comment note frontmatter\n- **Dark mode** — new Appearance setting: Follow Obsidian theme (auto), Always light, or Always dark\n- **Accent colour settings** — colour picker to customise the accent colour, or toggle to match Obsidian's accent colour automatically\n- **Centralised colour system** — all accent colours defined via CSS custom properties for consistency\n\n## Fixes\n\n- Comment preview text padding adjusted to avoid overlap with delete and expand buttons",
