      "author": "kirangathani",
      "description": "## What's New\n\n- **Collapsible comments**: Comments now collapse by default showing a 5-line preview, and expand when clicked or selected\n- **Comment cycling**: Alt+D / Alt+Shift+D navigates between comments with scroll sync\n- **Ctrl+F search**: Search overlay on the PDF viewer searches both PDF text and comment content. Enter/Shift+Enter to cycle matches, Escape to close\n- **Dynamic view title**: Tab header now shows the PDF filename instead of generic \"PDF viewer\"\n- **Delete button**: Comments now have a visible delete button on hover\n- **Wikilink suggest improvements**: Improved keyboard navigation in the autocomplete popup",
